Setting up Madek with Ansible
=============================

Usage
-----

### Install or Upgrade Madek

    ansible-playbook  -i hosts_vm play_setup-and-deploy.yml

### Set Admin Passord

    ansible-playbook  -i hosts_vm play_create-admin.yml -e 'admin_password=YOUR-SECRETE-PASSWORD'


